  05 Sep 2007; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> hoe-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #190161

  26 Aug 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> hoe-1.2.2.ebuild:
  ia64/x86 stable wrt #190161

*hoe-1.3.0 (15 Aug 2007)

  15 Aug 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +hoe-1.3.0.ebuild:
  Version bump:
   * Hoe now builds signed gems automatically.
   * Extended rdoc pattern to include ext dirs.
   * Fixed dependency adding for versionless dependencies.
   * Added NODOT env var to disable RDoc diagram generation.
   * The config_hoe task automatically merges in new config entries.

*hoe-1.2.2 (24 Jul 2007)

  24 Jul 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -hoe-1.1.6.ebuild,
  -hoe-1.2.0.ebuild, +hoe-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Version bump with minor bug fixes

*hoe-1.2.1 (04 Jun 2007)

  04 Jun 2007; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +hoe-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Version bump: 8 minor enhancements and 1 bug fix.

